verbose_text: Moreover, CsPDAT1-A expression resulted in obvious changes in fatty acid composition in the leaf, with ALA showing an increase by 45%, and correspondingly lower levels of saturated fatty acids (16:0, 18:0 and 20:0) and linoleic acid (18:2), than in the controls (XREF_FIG).
